Package cs350s21project.datatype

Class Altitude

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs350s21project.datatype.Altitude
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    I_Unitable<Altitude>, I_WorldCoordinatable, I_XMLable, java.lang.Comparable<Altitude>
    public class Altitude
extends java.lang.Object
implements I_Unitable<Altitude>, I_WorldCoordinatable, I_XMLable
    Defines an altitude. The units are assumed to be feet, but no calculations rely on this. It allows negative values to support delta values.
